rComments: Really nice, caring, great guy. He really wants everyone to understand and he will not let any student behind. He's a great teacher and don't get behind because he doesn't make it hard to get an A. If you understand it/try the whole time, you will be fine
I've never enjoyed math or thought I could be good at it.  Terry changed that.  He's a terrific teacher  who is funny, clear, and caring.  I'd take another class from him anytime.

I really liked Terry's approach to teaching the material. He made precalculus actually enjoyable. Terry should be teaching all the precalculus courses and teach any of the calculus series. The final was very straightforward. Everything he says that will be on the final ARE on the final. He gives students the benefit of the doubt. Great instructor!
